      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the \"it depends\" thing but looking at it logically, if we say it's a right, doesn't that mean the government *has* to provide it? whereas the other side says it just breaks the economy. if you had to weigh the two, which one actually makes more sense for a modern society?",
